{"tid":157903,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"揭發保良局領袖紀律訓練營的惡行","createTime":"2017-03-16T00:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T19:37:27.000Z","uid":12566,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"042825b7eef455a6c69bf2dd0f38343da85852f1","tid":157903,"uid":12566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T00:20:51.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係英華嗰位寫信揭發保良局領袖紀律訓練營嘅王同學。<br />\n<br />\n我留意到網上輿論常有出現學生在營中受到不合理、不人道對待嘅事件。我希望大家若果有相關證據，或者你曾經向校方、社工等相關人士舉報過，而又有報告嘅話，希望你哋將呢啲事件喺以下google form 詳細寫出，並留低聯絡方法。<br />\n<br />\n我會將收到嘅案例交俾立法會議員、記者，甚至警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n就算失望，不能絕望。香港學生加油！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfL2MFP3-4O1MIMpTIK5dTUSft9e_-22k3AZopXC2YaxDa_CA/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfL2MFP3-4O1MIMpTIK5dTUSft9e_-22k3AZopXC2YaxDa_CA%2Fviewform%3Fc%3D0%26w%3D1&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=77a5d976\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfL2MFP3-4O1MIMpTIK5dTUSft9e_-22k3AZopXC2YaxDa_CA/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1</a>"},{"pid":"723f5a39ff1b1c437534c04aa3e968dbb2d7f167","tid":157903,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T00:21:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc31b35541aef9bcd8001c4f5bc0c4d4b04dc41","tid":157903,"uid":2360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T00:53:59.000Z","msg":"Lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c1f6224cc16e833b63c6d408acf29a1db68325","tid":157903,"uid":12566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T02:08:00.000Z","msg":"仲未回應保良局<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170316&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56431671&amp;ref=tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170316%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56431671%26ref%3Dtw&